.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, brown, turquise, lavender, emerald
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, japanese, indian, indonesian, chinese
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, old-henry, davidoff, aristoff, cain
5 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, hamster, lizard, rat
1. the nigerian is the person who likes turquise
2. the swedish is the owner of the hamster
3. the japanese is the person drinking soy-milk
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes lavender
5. the person who likes brown is the person drinking lemonade
6. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the goat
7. the person who likes emerald is the old-henry-smoker
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the indonesian is on the far left
10. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret
11. the owner of the rats is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker
12. the havana-smoker is the person drinking mirinda
13. the indian is the aristoff-smoker
14. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who likes pink
15. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    emerald	|     pink	|      turquise	|     brown	|     lavender	|
| Nationality	|   indonesian	|    japanese	|    nigerian	|    indian	|    chinese	|
| Pet		|     ferret	|    rat	|     goat	|     lizard	|      hamster	|
| Beverage	|    hot-chocolate	|     soy-milk	|     almond-milk	|    lemonade	|      mirinda	|
| Cigar		|   old-henry	|    cain	|  davidoff	|    aristoff	|   havana	|
